---
title: Double Chocolate Brownies with Dark Chocolate Chunks | Serves 4+
description: Why eat chocolate when you can eat double chocolate! That’s why these chocolate brownies get sneaky white chocolate chips stirred into the mix. It takes hardly any effort to create a stunning effect on your brownies for a dessert with maximum wow-factor.

*This recipe makes 8-10 servings which is reflected in the nutritional information.*
